{"tid":148712,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"對我愛理 不理 我真係好難受","createTime":"2017-03-08T18:42:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-10T09:59:55.000Z","uid":41877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6c12f12bb1bb20e4ea8e55d6620449f4cbf41e0b","tid":148712,"uid":41877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T18:42:58.000Z","msg":"一齊左5年有多 同居左好耐<br />\n每日我地返工都好夜先收工 返到屋企 每日佢都會打機同男性朋友 打機唔係問題<br />\n所以由佢打 日子耐左 佢每日都係返工收工就打機沖涼之後訓教 <br />\n好想佢可以問下我今日點啊 其實我都係想佢關心下我 同我講多野 每晚訓教前都會覺得 其實係你都唔係好在乎我 <br />\n因為愛一個人係會想每日都關心佢每日發生d咩事 點解而個世界 愛與被愛係兩個世界既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f4ff5366f2ea0868237a94789f360dd35c1b0cd","tid":148712,"uid":64131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T18:54:19.000Z","msg":"所有問題都係女人諗出黎"},{"pid":"2d9d9c5bc0500a7eebc2d2cb30a99ccdfe58f028","tid":148712,"uid":41877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T18:58:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所有問題都係女人諗出黎</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />求解答"},{"pid":"2d0096a541942699ecfd594da3f493435c4bd2a0","tid":148712,"uid":55847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T08:06:45.000Z","msg":"當你肉便器囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你愛人會唔會咁先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aa30b02fa063ffdc7a438a620defcd805189ec1","tid":148712,"uid":41877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T09:59:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當你肉便器囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你愛人會唔會咁先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁佢又唔會 好細食<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}